<GRAPHIC>
<P>
Photo, Barbara Davis, left, and Valentino Garavani at celebratory dinner for 60 
at L'Orangerie following opening of his Valentino Boutique. GARY FRIEDMAN / Los 
Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
