Keith McDonald, whose pass fell incomplete. ; Photo, Wide receiver Marcus Tayui 
is dragged down after a short gain in second quarter of Esperanza's 25-7 
victory in Division III title game. JOHN FUNG / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
