PREP FOOTBALL ROUNDUP 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By DAVID RAATZ 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Temecula Valley 29, Palos Verdes 7 -- Ronnie Long ran for three touchdowns and 
intercepted three passes as Temecula Valley, only six years old, claimed its 
first CIF championship in the Southern Section Division VIII title game. 
</P>
<P>
It was the last football game for Palos Verdes (8-6), which is closing next 
year. 
</P>
<P>
Temecula Valley (11-3), took the lead for good at 10-7 on Long's two-yard run 
with 4:25 left in the first half. 
</P>
<P>
Long led the Bears with 83 yards in 16 carries. DAVID RAATZ 
