INVESTIGATIONS; POLITICAL CORRUPTION; CALIFORNIA -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; 
SUBPOENAS; GRAND JURIES; LEGISLATION -- CALIFORNIA; CONFLICT OF INTEREST; 
NORCAL SOLID WASTE SYSTEMS (COMPANY); DUMPS -- NORTHERN CALIFORNIA 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
