Photo, COLOR, (COVER) Black and white hands. Diego Uchitel; Photo, COLOR, 
Pascal Giacomini and Carine Fabius ; Photo, COLOR, Keith Kernan and Claudia 
Mitchell-Kernan ; Photo, COLOR, Alex and Margie Norman 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
