sufferer Ken Cooke, in wheelchair, dissolve in mirth as they sing at Ahimsa 
Care Center, a Laguna Beach facility for AIDS patients that has beds for 18 
people. ; Photo, Saline solution, then heparin, is injected into heart catheter 
of AIDS sufferer Matthew Hamlin. ; Photo, Matthew Hamlin, pictured on Oct. 31, 
